---

### [choco://intel-arc-graphics-driver](choco://intel-arc-graphics-driver/s=https://nuts.bcurran3.org/nuget/chocolatey/)
To use choco:// protocol URLs, install [choco:// Protocol support ](https://nuts.bcurran3.org/feeds/chocolatey/choco-protocol-support/versions)


---

This download installs Intel Arc Graphics Driver xx.xx.xx.xx for Intel® Arc™ Graphics family (Codename Alchemist, Battlemage)and Intel® Core™ Ultra processor family (Codename Meteor Lake, Lunar Lake, Arrow Lake-S, Arrow Lake-H)


